Show Info

Los Angeles

The former EastEnder visits Los Angeles, which is home to over 1,000
gangs with more than 100,000 members, and where a related murder
happens every other day. He joins the LAPD on patrol and meets those
involved in the battles between the infamous Bloods and the Crips, as
well as exploring the emergence of Latino gangs
